OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FA newly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,8,Fin Plymouth has been suspended by the
OL,9,Fparty just days after winning his seat
OL,10,Fin the local elections.
OL,12,FBen Rowe, who was elected to represent
OL,13,FHam ward on Plymouth City Council last
OL,14,Fweek, is now the subject of an
OL,15,Finternal investigation after a series
OL,16,Fof social media posts he allegedly
OL,17,Fmade resurfaced online.
OL,19,FIt is claimed the posts contain
OL,20,Fracist, antisemitic and Islamophobic
OL,21,Fcomments.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
