PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FReform UK confirmed on Monday (May 11)
OL,8,Fthat Rowe had been suspended pending
OL,9,Fan investigation.
OL,11,FA party spokesperson said the matter
OL,12,Fwas being looked into and that the
OL,13,Fsuspension would remain in place while
OL,14,Fenquiries continue.
OL,16,FThe controversy comes less than a week
OL,17,Fafter Reform celebrated strong
OL,18,Felection results across parts of
OL,19,FEngland, including gains in Plymouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
