FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FThe party has sought to position
OL,8,Fitself as a growing political force
OL,9,Fahead of future national elections,
OL,10,Fbut the suspension risks overshadowing
OL,11,Fthat momentum.
OL,13,FPolitical opponents have already
OL,14,Fcalled for further scrutiny over how
OL,15,Fcandidates are vetted before standing
OL,16,Ffor office.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
