PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FThe latest row has also renewed wider
OL,8,Fquestions around Reform UK's candidate
OL,9,Fselection process after similar
OL,10,Fallegations emerged elsewhere in the
OL,11,Fcountry involving other newly elected
OL,12,Frepresentatives.
OL,14,FLabour leader of Plymouth City Council
OL,15,FTudor Evans, previously said the
OL,16,Fcomments were "utterly reprehensible
OL,17,Fand have no place in Plymouth".
OL,26,@xD@OOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
