PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FHe added: "Encouraging violence
OL,8,Fagainst a place of worship, spreading
OL,9,Fantisemitic conspiracy theories,
OL,10,Fdehumanising immigrants, and using
OL,11,Fracist and Islamophobic language is
OL,12,Fnot only deeply offensive, but also
OL,13,Fdangerous."
OL,15,FMP for Plymouth and Devonport Luke
OL,16,FPollard, said in a post on X:
OL,17,F"Disturbing to see the new Reform
OL,18,Fcouncillor for Ham Ward suspended for
OL,19,Foffensive comments just days after the
OL,20,Fcount.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
