PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,F"Plymouth is a city of "Janner"
OL,8,Fspirit, we look after one another.
OL,9,FHatred and division have no place
OL,10,Frepresenting us."
OL,12,FWhen the alleged comments first
OL,13,Femerged, Councillor Steven Ricketts,
OL,14,FReform Leader in Plymouth City Council
OL,15,Fsaid: "My party is thoroughly
OL,16,Finvestigating and this is with the
OL,17,Fdisciplinary team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778764275
OL,3,CNewly elected Reform UK councillor
OL,4,Csuspended over alleged social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,F"There is a process and that will be
OL,8,Ffollowed in this case - I can't
OL,9,Fcomment further than that at this
OL,10,Ftime."
OL,12,FThe Ham ward result was one of several
OL,13,Fclosely watched contests in Plymouth
OL,14,Fduring this year's local elections,
OL,15,Fwith voters across the city helping
OL,16,Freshape the political balance on the
OL,17,Fcouncil.
OL,19,FBen Rowe has not yet responded to the
OL,20,Fallegations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
